<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reminder: Your Upcoming Paper Mastery Consultation Session</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #4F46E5;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .session-details {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .session-details h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #4F46E5;
        }
        .session-details p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .session-details strong {
            color: #111827;
        }
        .zoom-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4F46E5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .reminder-badge {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            color: #92400E;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6B7280;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Session Reminder</h1>
        <div class="reminder-badge">
            {% if hours_before == 1 %}
            Starts in 1 hour
            {% else %}
            Starts in {{ hours_before }} hours
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello{% if user_name %} {{ user_name }}{% endif %},</p>
        
        <p>
            This is a reminder that your consultation session with 
            {% if researcher_name %}<strong>{{ researcher_name }}</strong>{% else %}a researcher{% endif %}
            {% if paper_title %}about "<strong>{{ paper_title }}</strong>"{% endif %} 
            is scheduled to begin in {{ hours_before }} hour{% if hours_before != 1 %}s{% endif %}.
        </p>
        
        <div class="session-details">
            <h2>Session Details</h2>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ date }}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{ time }}</p>
            <p><strong>Session ID:</strong> {{ session_id }}</p>
            
            {% if zoom_link %}
            <p><strong>Zoom Link:</strong></p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ zoom_link }}" class="zoom-button">Join Zoom Meeting</a>
            </p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <h3>Quick Checklist</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensure your internet connection is stable</li>
            <li>Test your camera and microphone</li>
            <li>Have any questions ready</li>
            <li>Find a quiet place for your session</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>
            We recommend joining the session 5 minutes early to ensure everything 
            is working properly.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact us at 
            <a href="mailto:{{ support_email }}">{{ support_email }}</a>.
        </p>
        <p>&copy; {{ current_year }} {{ platform_name }}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 